resources.name: get all products
resources.description:
1. Get product by category in related store
    {{ _.baseurl }}/product?storeId=1&categoryId=1
  2. Get product by category in all store
    {{ _.baseurl }}/product?categoryId=1
  3. Get store product and sort by desc rating
    {{ _.baseurl }}/product?storeId=1&order=rating:desc
  4. Get all product and sort by desc rating
    {{ _.baseurl }}/product?order=rating:desc
All query string function works on this endpoint, u choose
